[p 
	[em 
		"A-mazing Tater
	]em
	" is a puzzle game released by Atlus in 1992. It is the sequel to 
	[a class=intlink href=/857M 
		"Kwirk
	]a
	", otherwise known as 
	[em 
		"Puzzle Boy
	]em
	" in Japan.  The player has to guide a small potato to the exit of each level, which is made difficult by a number of obstacles, most notoriously crates.
]p
